a crime and I would hate to see it.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the countries\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"these really rough areas\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1658}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medals\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"a crime\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully they can nut it out, I truly believe they will.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxing deserves to be in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boxing\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has saved many people's lives and I have seen it save many people's lives.\\\"\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many people's lives\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"many people's lives\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Men's boxing first featured in the modern Olympics in 1904, while women have been on the card since 2016.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Men's boxing\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1974}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern Olympics\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"the card\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's boxing team captain, Caitlin Parker, is one of six Aussie women competing in the sport at the Games.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2069, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8708468967773022, \"rank\": 0.14402884477572686, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\"